column2: select my.*,SpecObj.*, galSpecExtra.*, galSpecIndx.*, galSpecInfo.*, galSpecLine.*,PhotoObj.*   into mydb.HSC_SDSS_cat   from mydb.HSC_SDSS as my     JOIN SpecObj on my.id = SpecObj.bestObjID     left join galSpecExtra on galSpecExtra.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID     left join galSpecIndx on galSpecIndx.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID     left join galSpecInfo on galSpecInfo.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID     left join galSpecLine on galSpecLine.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID     left join PhotoObj on PhotoObj.objID = SpecObj.bestObjID
